This is the 2nd version of my race_island and maybe the final one.
So you ask whats new in this version?
Here's the changelog

Changelog of version 2
- Fixed minor bugs
- Added a beach zone with a ready zone(now there are 2 ready zones. One near the spawn and other in the beach)
- Added 1 more lap to the existing 3(Medium time of the 4 laps 2:50:00)
- Added FRAGXL.com bilboards

What didn't change?

- Gman for spectator zone
- A fun wait zone
- The 4 Pit Stops

For now it's all hope you enjoy ;)
----------------------------
In order to play this map, you need Rally Race Mod installed in your server. If you want to play this map, you can join FRAGXL.com | Rally RaceMania - 80.172.230.146:27015
